@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@token =

### ================== INCIDENCIAS ==================

### Obtener todas las incidencias
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidences
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear una incidencia
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incidences
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "busId": 1,
  "routeId": 1,
  "description": "Retraso por tráfico pesado",
  "severity": "MEDIA",
  "status": "ACTIVO",
  "reportedAt": "2024-09-15T07:30:00Z",
  "reportedBy": "Operador",
  "actionsTaken": "Se notificó a los padres"
}

###

### Obtener incidencia por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidences/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar una incidencia
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/incidences/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "busId": 1,
  "routeId": 1,
  "description": "Retraso por tráfico resuelto",
  "severity": "MEDIA",
  "status": "ACTIVO",
  "reportedAt": "2024-09-15T07:30:00Z",
  "resolvedAt": "2024-09-15T08:30:00Z",
  "reportedBy": "Operador",
  "actionsTaken": "Se ajustó el horario"
}

###

### Eliminar una incidencia físicamente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/incidences/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Eliminar una incidencia lógicamente
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/incidences/1/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
